<!-- wp:heading {"level":1} -->
<h1>Bronze Medallion</h1>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"fontSize":16}}} -->
<p style="font-size:16px;"><span class="has-inline-color has-foreground-light-color">Bronze & SRC week</span><br><strong>Monday 16 - Saturday 21 December 2019 @ Ocean Grove Surf Lifesaving Club, 28 Surf Beach Rd Ocean Grove</strong><br>Registrations are now open and will close Friday 6 December. Depending on numbers as at 5 December, we may accept members of other local surf clubs.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><a href="http://www">2019/20 Bronze/SRC Week General Info</a><br><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="http://www." target="_blank">2019/20 Bronze/SRC Week Timetable</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>WHAT IS SRC AND BRONZE MEDALLON?<br>The Surf Rescue Certificate (SRC) and Bronze Medallion (BM) are the base-level surf lifesaving awards required to participate as a team member in a surf life saving service (patrol). Ocean Grove SLSC expects that all members aged 13+ will gain their SRC/Bronze Medallion and patrol at least 16 hours per season. Candidates will learn about; surf awareness, CPR, administering oxygen and defibrillation, First Aid, Radio Operations, board rescue techniques, carriers and support, and beach management.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>SRC is the base award for members 13 - 14 years to be able to patrol.<br>Bronze Medallion is the base awards for members 15 years and over to be able to patrol.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>To be elligible for the course you must:<br>- Be a current financial member of Ocean Grove SLSC (or another Victorian SLSC)<br>- Meet required age (i.e. must have turned 13 or 15 no more than 60 days after 21 DecemebrDecember)</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong><span class=&quot;has-inline-color has-primary-color&quot;>FITNESS REQUIREMENTS</span></strong><br></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:table {&quot;backgroundColor&quot;:&quot;subtle-pale-blue&quot;,&quot;className&quot;:&quot;is-style-stripes&quot;} -->
<figure class=&quot;wp-block-table is-style-stripes&quot;><table class=&quot;has-subtle-pale-blue-background-color has-background&quot;><thead><tr><th></th><th>Pool Swim</th><th>Beach Run-Swim-Run</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Bronze Medallion</td><td>400m in 9 minutes</td><td>200m run, 200m swim, 200m run</td></tr><tr><td>SRC</td><td>200m in 5 minutes</td><td>100m run, 100m swim, 100mrun</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>
<!-- /wp:table -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong><span class=&quot;has-inline-color has-primary-color&quot;>COSTS</span></strong><br>Course price: $300 including brunch, lunch and a/tea each day. Bronze Week hoodies are optional extras - $60.<br>Each day is 7:30 am - 5:00 pm (apart from a later finish on Wednesday)</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong><span class=&quot;has-inline-color has-primary-color&quot;>HOW TO REGISTER</span></strong><br>1. Renew membership or join OGSLSC. <a href=&quot;https://oceangroveslsccom.wordpress.com/membership/&quot;>Click here for more membership information.</a><br>2. Follow <a href=&quot;http://www.&quot;>these instructions</a> to register online through LSV Member Training from Anywhere portal and to pay online to Ocean Grove SLSC.<br>3. Email <a href=&quot;mailto:admin@oceangroveslsc.asn.au&quot;>admin@oceangroveslsc.asn.au</a> with the participant's name, confirm that you have registered and paid and any dietary requirements. Indicate whether you want to purchase a SRC/Bronze Week Hoodie, specifying size.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>For questions about the registration process, please contact Anna our Administrator at <a href=&quot;mailto:admin@oceangroveslsc.asn.au&quot;>admin@oceangroveslsc.asn.au</a>.<br>For questions about the course, please contact me on <a href=&quot;mailto:instructor@oceangroveslsc.asn.au&quot;>instructor@oceangroveslsc.asn.au</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {&quot;style&quot;:{&quot;typography&quot;:{&quot;fontSize&quot;:18}}} -->
<p style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;><span class=&quot;has-inline-color has-primary-color&quot;>Adult Bronze Course</span><br>We conducted a course in October 2019.<br>Enquiries email <a href=&quot;mailto:amenah@y7mail.com&quot;>amenah@y7mail.com</a> </p>
